Instar 3 premoult caterpillar of 
<taxonomicName box="[619,809,751,774]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Perrotia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="326" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="albiplaga">
<emphasis box="[619,809,751,774]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="326">Perrotia albiplaga</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
collected and photographed 16 Aug 1990 on? 
<taxonomicName authority="Andasibe" authorityName="Andasibe" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Decaryochloa" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="25" pageNumber="326" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="diadelpha">
